project_descr: This component of the electoral cycle programme aims to support the development of a national decentralized system for transmitting and collating election results.

donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)
outputs.output_descr: The project aims to support the development of a nationally decentralized system for transmitting and collating election results as well as provide accurate and up to date information on Election Day events across the country.
